<br />
The main strategy is to choke opponent and run with hobbit<br />
<br />
Companion <br />
Frodo , 11 str with promise,sword<br />
Sam , 9 with sword and promise<br />
Merry , 9 with sword and armor<br />
Pippin , 10 with sword, armor and 3 threats<br />
<br />
These hobbit are huge and can win many skirmish, PATH  help you to kill minion that have a lot of vitality or exhausted minion.<br />
<br />
Don&#39;t hesistate to use there and back again often , there are 3 in the deck and they are unique so better use them.<br />
<br />
If you begin, plas sword on pippin and merry and remove 2, sword on frodo will be free. Mulligann if you dont have a talent for not being seen<br />
<br />
Usualy this go 1-3, 3-4,4-5,(Sometime 3-5),5-7(Doubling site 6 heal every hobbit),7-8,8-9 or 7-9, be sure to be the first at site 7 and you allmost win the game<br />
<br />
Trackers <br />
Brought back alive can kill pesky merry and pippin <br />
I forgot &quot;Caradhras has not forgiven us&quot; in the deck list, this card is huge. Discard a starting a companion and its like you kill him. Searcher can kill 2 companion is there is 2 weary. Palantir is there slow the opponent deck ,this way he wont discard big minion and he can&#39;t play thme because of the choke hobbit<br />
<br />
This deck is really fun to play but not for opponent, play it only if you like to be insulted ;p<br />
